---
shc
-- interchangeably configurable shell compiler
---- supersedes ://shm
---
Use
-- provides more advanced distribution options for sh scripts 
---- by adding a compilation layer
-- uses `Syntax Files` to compile custom syntax back to POSIX sh
---- allows for custom features, short-hands, style enforcement and more
---
Plans
-- configurable compiler options
---- options to enable/disable features
-- 100% reconfigurable
---- `Syntax Files` allow configuration of everything
---- compile any code base to shell!
---
